---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Purchase confirmed | Sky Lavelle"
  description="Your template pack purchase is confirmed."
  noindex
>
  <section class="section min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="container max-w-2xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-3">Purchase confirmed.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-700">
          Your download link has been sent to your email. If you do not see it within a few minutes, check your spam folder.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 p-6 mb-6 bg-warm-50">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">Getting the most from your pack</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-warm-800">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ochre-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Start with the guidance notes before adapting any template.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ochre-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            All documents are fully editable. Remove or add sections to match your situation.
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ochre-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            If your situation needs senior delivery support alongside the templates, an advisory review is available through Lavelle Pty Ltd.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <a
          href="https://lavelleptyltd.com.au/consulting"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100 hover:bg-warm-200 transition-colors"
        >
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-1">Need advisory support?</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-800 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Senior consulting and contract project management services through Lavelle Pty Ltd.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">View consulting &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/articles" class="group flex flex-col p-5 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white hover:border-ochre-400 transition-colors">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-1">Related articles</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed flex-1">
            Practical guides on project recovery, business cases, procurement and steering committee reporting.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-ochre-600">Browse articles &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
